          </svg>
        </div>
        <h4>Parking</h4>
        <p>Plenty of free on-site parking at the front and back of the clinic, as well as off-street parking nearby.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="getting-here-card">
        <div class="icon">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
